<br>
Why won't Iraq be deterred where the Soviet Union was Aybolit?  They're less of a threat, they're not a nuclear power so can't even mutually deter the US/UK, it's not even certain whether their WMD are in a fit state to be used!  Surely such a defanged dictator desperate to survive as he is, can be deterred?<br>
