Now on to an interesting couple snippets:<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>USSR collapsed because it could no longer afford it's highly corrupted elite and it's centralized economics structure. Those two simply cannot coexist<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
