Under sanctions and under threat of violent reprisal, Saddam is being effectively contained.  Not a single person on this thread has managed to prove that containment has failed.  And as for why don't we just &quot;do it&quot;- if it ain't broke, why fix it?  Containment works- it'll take more than suspicion or conjecture to convince me or any sane individual of its failure.<br>
